Class ItemList

java.lang.Object
org.drip.service.representation.ItemList
public class ItemList
extends java.lang.Object
ItemList is an Adaptation of the ItemList Interface from the RFC4627 compliant JSON Simple (https://code.google.com/p/json-simple/). |a:b:c| = |a|,|b|,|c| |:| = ||,|| |a:| = |a|,||
